有离开过郑州市而且据我所知最近郑州也没有疫情。河南村镇银行储户：卡里只有两毛钱存款，但我的健康码还是红了三天 _ 上观新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-34a72f9e6349f46c503ca9178224c140_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "173 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/537985026"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is5qC+dfc36N7EAMaCDgxODM0MTgwIKDnqpUGMAo41wFADXIJNTM3OTg1MDI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1655464088.1098013", "card_id": "Q_538145119", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 208}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "NBA 金州勇士当家球星斯蒂芬·库里，8 年 6 总决赛 4 次总冠军 1 次 FMVP，如何评价其历史地位？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1617c6b3f68559912479402824373c4e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "172 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/538145119"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Is5qC+dfc36N7EAMaCDgxODY5Njk3IM3rr5UGMAw40AJADnIJNTM4MTQ1MTE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1655464088.1102095", "card_id": "Q_538120561", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 762}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "媒体报道上海解封后不见「报复性消费」 ，经济复苏步伐缓慢，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "上海本月 1 日解封后，冷清了两个月的街道重现人潮，购物商场门前也排起等待入场的长龙。但半个月过去，「报复性消费」现象不如预期强劲。这不仅拖累这个经济重镇的复苏步伐，也令中国整体经济面对更大压力。 来源：早报网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-d0a4d349b3763d889cad939a1a9563be_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "155 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/538120561"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIs5qC+dfc36N7EAMaCDgxODY0MT